{
  "texts": [
    "Moreover, even without any labeled examples, LLM reasoning also improves the accuracy to 69.68.",
    "A similar trend is observed on Gossicop, though not on Fakeddit.",
    "We hypothesize that this is due to the lower overlap between the pretraining data of Qwen3-8B and Fakeddit compared to other two subsets.2.",
    "Supervised learning remains effective.",
    "Emb+GNN consistently outperforms Qwen3-8B-based methods across all three subsets."
  ]
}